  <body>
    <div class="sticky-access" role="navigation" aria-label="Quick links">
      <a class="sticky-access__link" href="../bio.html">Meet Monty</a>
    </div>
    <header class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="back-link" href="../index.html">Back to Monty's archive</a>
        <h1>The Charity Safari</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          Monty's 1992 safari fundraiser blended conservation rhetoric with air-conditioned jeeps, ensuring donors never
          broke a sweat while saving the savanna.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="cards-grid expanded-grid" aria-label="Charity safari details">
        <article class="card" id="csf-memory-01">
          <div class="card-link">
            <h2>VIP Itinerary</h2>
            <p class="card-meta"><span class="meta-label">ID:</span> CSF-01 <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> <span class="meta-label">Date:</span> June 3, 1992</p>
            <p>
              Guests received monogrammed binoculars, chilled champagne, and a schedule of “curated
              animal encounters.” Zebra Montgomery had four wardrobe changes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card" id="csf-memory-02">
          <div class="card-link">
            <h2>Beneficiary Breakdown</h2>
            <p class="card-meta"><span class="meta-label">ID:</span> CSF-02 <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> <span class="meta-label">Date:</span> June 5, 1992</p>
            <p>
              Proceeds funded the zebra's private habitat, complete with a personal groomer.
              Remaining funds purchased themed safari murals for donors' foyers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card" id="csf-memory-03">
          <div class="card-link">
            <h2>Media Reception</h2>
            <p class="card-meta"><span class="meta-label">ID:</span> CSF-03 <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> <span class="meta-label">Date:</span> August 10, 1992</p>
            <p>
              Society pages praised the glamour while conservationists requested more actual
              conservation. Monty responded with a limited-edition coffee-table book.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card" id="csf-memory-04">
          <div class="card-link">
            <h2>Sunset Gala Encore</h2>
            <p class="card-meta"><span class="meta-label">ID:</span> CSF-04 <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> <span class="meta-label">Date:</span> July 14, 1992</p>
            <p>
              He staged a sunset encore featuring choreographed lantern releases shaped like safari
              animals, each representing a donor tier.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card" id="csf-memory-05">
          <div class="card-link">
            <h2>After-Action Chronicle</h2>
            <p class="card-meta"><span class="meta-label">ID:</span> CSF-05 <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> <span class="meta-label">Date:</span> September 1, 1993</p>
            <p>
              The following year he published a leather-bound chronicle with watercolor maps and
              hand-written thank-yous, ensuring every patron’s adventure felt canonized.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="page-footer">
      <div class="container">
        <p>Expanded archive entry for Monty's charity safari.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
